result.title: szkopul.edu.pl not showing judge info for new problems
result.content: When I submitted code that was previously successfully submitted on main, szkopul bugs out; I get INI_ERR with no other information (Little Bird, POI 21) or INI_OK (Couriers, POI 21). Scores do not appear for either of these problems. The older problems I submitted for contained error information and scores, but it seems that these problems do not. Is there any known solution?
